INSTRUCTIONS.md: Corporate-Life T‑Shirt E‑Commerce (Production Build Spec)
Purpose of this file: This is a self-contained, hand-off-ready build specification for an AI coding agent (Claude Code or similar) to design and build the entire product end-to-end. It is written to be granular and unambiguous. Where a decision is required, this doc makes a recommendation and marks it [DECISION]. Where the human owner must supply a value, it is marked [OWNER-INPUT]. Do not invent secrets, API keys, or legal text — flag them.

Locked decisions (from owner):

Stack: Custom Next.js (not Shopify).
Primary market: India — Razorpay + UPI, INR, GST.
Auto-generation: AI slogans + auto-mockup, with a mandatory admin approval step.
Fulfillment: Print-on-demand (POD) specced now, wired later. Launch = manual/self-fulfill.

Golden rules for the building agent:

Do not hallucinate APIs, prices, or library behavior — verify against current docs before use.
Ship the MVP (Phase 1) first; everything else is behind feature flags.
Every edgy slogan passes through a moderation gate before it can go live.
Mobile-first. Gen Z buys on phones. The "crazy graphics" must degrade gracefully.
No secret is ever committed. All secrets via .env + a deployment secret manager.


